'''城山子山城'''是[[渤海国|渤海国]]的早期[[都城|都城]]，遗址位于[[中国|中国]][[吉林省|吉林省]][[敦化市|敦化市]]西南。

==布局==
城山子山城分内外二城，城垣版筑。外城东西400米，南北200米，东墙已毁。内城正方形，边长80米，位于外城中偏西，外建[[护城壕|护城壕]]。地势高于外城。内外城南门相对，向西南有通往[[扶余府|扶余府]]（今农安）的道路。<ref>{{cite web|author=考古|title=吉林敦化牡丹江上游渤海遗址调查记|url=http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=46&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=KAGU196211006&dbname=CJFD7984&dbcode=CJFQ&pr=&urlid=&yx=&v=MjMyNDV4WVM3RGgxVDNxVHJXTTFGckNVUkw2ZmIrWm9GQ25oVmJ2Qkxpek1lN0t4R05QTnJvOUZZb1I4ZVgxTHU=|accessdate=1962年11期|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304194613/http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=46&CurRec=1&recid=&filename=KAGU196211006&dbname=CJFD7984&dbcode=CJFQ&pr=&urlid=&yx=&v=MjMyNDV4WVM3RGgxVDNxVHJXTTFGckNVUkw2ZmIrWm9GQ25oVmJ2Qkxpek1lN0t4R05QTnJvOUZZb1I4ZVgxTHU=|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>

